  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is an observational study designed to follow patients with metastatic or locally
      advanced and unresectable colorectal cancer who are receiving Avastin in combination with
      chemotherapy and whose cancer has been either previously untreated or treated &lt;=4 months
      prior to enrollment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
